 Guiledart walked up to Galvatron. "There is no need for the cr chamber." he 
pulled out a needle and jammed it into Galvatron's arm. He dint flinch a 
second. "What is it." Suddenly all his wound healed up and he was back to 
100%. "It is the enrgon you need to use that healing abililty you inherited 
from the predacon. Whenever you need just ask."

--part1_a1.105dde68.27a4548d_boundary
